Sentencas: La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+delta system was successfully synthesized by a modified Pechini route in air.
Titulo: Study of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+δ series as potential cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A structural phase transition is observed along the series, from tetragonal ordered structure for 0 <= x <= 2 to a rhombohedral disordered perovskite for x = 5.
Titulo: Study of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+δ series as potential cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A TEC value of 17.3 x 10(-6) K-1, was found by High-Temperature X-ray Diffraction (HT-XRD) in air for La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+delta.
Titulo: Study of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+δ series as potential cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The conductivity of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+delta increases with temperature reaching a maximum of 778 S cm(-1) at 405 degrees C in air followed by a decrease with further increase in temperature with values of 600-664 S cm(-1).
Titulo: Study of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+δ series as potential cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The cathode polarization resistance of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+delta evaluated in air at 750 degrees C is 0.34 Omega cm(2) with an activation energy of 1.65 eV.
Titulo: Study of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+δ series as potential cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: These results demonstrate the possible use of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+delta materials as cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: Study of La4BaCu5-xCoxO13+δ series as potential cathode materials for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell
